utive, historian and philanthropher<ref>[http://www.allaccess.com/net-news/archive/story/124417/remembering-jerry-boulding Remembering Jerry Boulding] from All Access (November 29, 2013)</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''December 15'''\n|[[Harold Camping]]\n|92\n|American minister/preacher and founder/owner of [[Family Radio]]<ref>[http://hosted-p0.vresp.com/1030185/5988170fbb/ARCHIVE Harold Camping-Home With The Lord] from Family Radio Website (December 16, 2013)</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''December 18'''\n|[[Larry Lujack]]\n|73\n|American radio personality, nicknamed \"Superjock\" during his tenure at [[WLS (AM)|WLS]] and [[WCFL (AM)|WCFL]]/Chicago<ref>[http://www.robertfeder.com/2013/12/18/larry-lujack-1940-2013/ Larry Lujack 1940-2013] from RobertFeder.com (December 18, 2013)</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''December 18'''\n|[[Ken Hutcherson]]\n|61\n|American professional football player, minister and frequent guest on the ''[[Glenn Beck Program]]'' and ''[[The Rush Limbaugh Show]]''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theblaze.com/stories/2013/12/18/pastor-and-former-nfl-player-ken-hutcherson-passes-away-at-age-61/ |title=Pastor and Former NFL Player Ken Hutcherson Passes Away At Age 61 |publisher=theblaze.com |accessdate=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219060219/http://www.theblaze.com/stories/2013/12/18/pastor-and-former-nfl-player-ken-hutcherson-passes-away-at-age-61/ |archive-date=2013-12-19 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''December 21'''\n|[[Geoff Stirling]]\n|92\n|Canadian multimedia mogul, owner of [[CHOZ-FM]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vocm.com/newsarticle.asp?mn=2&ID=41841 |title=NL Broadcasting Icon Geoff Stirling Dead at 92 |date=December 22, 2013 |accessdate=December 22, 2013 |publisher=[[VOCM (AM)|VOCM]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224112832/http://www.vocm.com/newsarticle.asp?mn=2&ID=41841 |archivedate=December 24, 2013 }}</