eabag, Watchmen, When They See Us, Unbelievable Among TV Nominees |website=TVLine |date=December 8, 2019 |accessdate=December 8, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[26th Screen Actors Guild Awards|Screen Actors Guild Awards]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sagawards.org/media/news/releases/nominations-announced-26th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE |title=NOMINATIONS ANNOUNCED FOR THE 26TH ANNUAL SCREEN ACTORS GUILD AWARDS |date=December 11, 2019 |accessdate=December 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Casting Society of America]]\n| Television Pilot & First Season \u2013 Comedy\n| Sherry Thomas, Sharon Bialy and Russell Scott\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/casting-society-tv-theatre-artios-awards-nominations-complete-list-1242878 | title = Artios Awards: 'Succession,' 'Pose,' 'Dead to Me' Among Casting Society TV, Theater Nominees |first = Hillary | last = Lewis | date = September 24, 2019 |work = [[The Hollywood Reporter]] | access-date = February 2, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Writers Guild of America Awards 2019|Writers Guild of America Awards]]\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: New Series|Television: New Series]]\n| [[Rebecca Addelman]], Njeri Brown, [[Liz Feldman]], Kelly Hutchinson, [[Anthony King (writer)|Anthony King]], Emma Rathbone, [[Kate Robin]] and Abe Sylvia\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/writers-guild-awards-2020-tv-nominations-1203426148/ |title=Writers Guild Unveils 2020 TV Award Nominees |first=Dave |last=McNary |date=December 5, 2019 |accessdate=December 5, 2019 |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Episodic Comedy|Television: Episodic Comedy]]\n| Liz Feldma